{"tid":156350,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑有性病....有無巴絲解答下我","createTime":"2017-03-14T16:03:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T03:04:31.000Z","uid":33991,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"16399963e5a9ddaf44fae974460ee47414159ab3","tid":156350,"uid":33991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:03:36.000Z","msg":"對唔住做左標題黨<br />\n做過兩次pap test<br />\n當中相隔一年左右, 兩次結果都係意義未明的非典型鱗狀上皮細胞(ASCUS)<br />\n簡單d姐係細胞病變<br />\n感染到hpv既機會好高...<br />\nhpv分高危同低危(椰菜花)<br />\n懷疑自己又高危hpv, 唔會生椰菜花唔會有病征, ,對男性完全無害, 但會大大提高自身罹患子宮頸癌既機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想請問各位巴絲知唔知道邊度有得做hpv dna test<br />\n上網搵好多資料都只係for男性低危...有無人有類似經驗可以話我知邊度有得做tets"},{"pid":"b8035b403a2eef7e9a2965bfbd17a09fba6e4c92","tid":156350,"uid":33991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:03:48.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"3e5351598b205bb94039ad8a9282f5e0e4f3098c","tid":156350,"uid":33991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:07:22.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"9b143744a2060ecef6be76f434c321232ce5565a","tid":156350,"uid":33991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:11:03.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"6f1c2d3dc4fdfc344b3f34c3eb866d7bfe809aec","tid":156350,"uid":33991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:12:40.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"ebdd7c8c7012f29816a94530001f5134f9ffe909","tid":156350,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:15:25.000Z","msg":"點解唔去問醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ecd4c344adf2dc3fde9553a1843a77c6571182","tid":156350,"uid":76488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:16:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b72ecf73b354857d4b72b9263217403a806ebb75","tid":156350,"uid":33991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:18:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔去問醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去左睇政府衛生科<br />\n係無得做hpv dna test<br />\n佢話得私家有，我上黎問問知唔知邊度有女性既hpv dna test做<br />\n因為google唔到，就算有都係二千幾三千蚊一個package, 包含一大堆我唔需要做既test, 而且afford唔到"},{"pid":"06416a4c7924c35ced1cb7285ac0e28f5b88761e","tid":156350,"uid":33991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:22:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>臭閪</blockquote><br />\n對唔住<br />\n其實80%有過性行為既女性都會感染到hpv病毒<br />\n仲要大部分人唔知，只有做過抹片檢查先有機會發現<br />\n病毒係無藥食，但大部分人身體免疫系統兩年內會清到病毒<br />\n我有左成年，仲要唔知幾時感染<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對唔住係我自身免疫力唔好同埋唔係處 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不撚好意思<br />\n如果係男性最好都去check check 無病征但係搞到條女有事你都唔好意思啦"},{"pid":"d99d82d429b99fd70fb74f4a7d4914ab50e114cf","tid":156350,"uid":33991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:25:57.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"5d450f6db58f7ca40003611c94797e5ba2cab4a4","tid":156350,"uid":33991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:27:49.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"7df1e9ec32d7b2bb65af2f59c673feb863ecc9c9","tid":156350,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:28:18.000Z","msg":"hiv同hpv有咩分別"},{"pid":"44cf8ce094691924df3260180d462df9f350dae2","tid":156350,"uid":51571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:28:43.000Z","msg":"絲打舊登有個post 入面有哂資料 你搵一搵啦"},{"pid":"1482c7939c6443e0a2bfa5ed0cfdec7907539ffa","tid":156350,"uid":51571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:32:35.000Z","msg":"btw 廢事post link 你google 舊登 性病拎<br />\n<br />\n利申：無中過 只係好奇入過去。希望幫到你"},{"pid":"c8078f96314aeb5ac2e5438d9649d57aa92b2e4e","tid":156350,"uid":33991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:33:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>hiv同hpv有咩分別</blockquote><br />\nhiv係愛滋病毒 係令你自身免疫力下降 好難好返<br />\nhpv係人類乳突瘤病毒(好似係) , 低危hpv會生椰菜花，無害，但有礙美觀同埋會傳染<br />\n高危hpv唔會生野，對女性會大大提高生子宮頸癌既機會，男性都可以感染，但無害，只會傳染比女性<br />\nhpv要靠自身免疫力好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de2ed2e6c6a00f9b5f71bc99e92eb88e336a5162","tid":156350,"uid":33991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:35:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw 廢事post link 你google 舊登 性病拎<br />\n<br />\n利申：無中過 只係好奇入過去。希望幫到你</blockquote><br />\n我有爬過曬po 咩性病集中討論區 但係入面全部都係巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地講既診所我眼見都係得男性做既hpv test,所以再開po問個清楚"},{"pid":"7337f968dbffe9beb4125a6db99ab081ddd1c87d","tid":156350,"uid":33991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:36:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw 廢事post link 你google 舊登 性病拎<br />\n<br />\n利申：無中過 只係好奇入過去。希望幫到你</blockquote><br />\n唔該曬你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2927b8b3710e8b2a965242c77b5af6cc00c0b06a","tid":156350,"uid":30001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:39:31.000Z","msg":"有間好似叫嘉怡女士健康中心<br />\n係隔離post好多人去既MHS 姊妹公司（好似係）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c7a544ad45556c877740947b0f91d40fbc95288","tid":156350,"uid":33991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:39:40.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"a32800f1274c0f976d0b2d5fce954ba1081fd61b","tid":156350,"uid":33991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:46:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有間好似叫嘉怡女士健康中心<br />\n係隔離post好多人去既MHS 姊妹公司（好似係）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 終於有想要既答案<br />\n但係我見個度有分<br />\n人類乳頭狀瘤病毒測試(package$2480)<br />\n人類乳頭瘤病毒 DNA 基因分型(package$980)<