有冇平啲介紹"},{"pid":"bbf12b0dd5ef93f8cf5451cb7c4874e2c1829fdc","tid":156350,"uid":88860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T00:45:49.000Z","msg":"你依家做HPV DNA (得私家先有）無用<br />\n因為HPV DNA係陰道鏡既alternative黎after you have an ASCUS in pap smear<br />\n玩法<br />\n1. ASCUS on pap---&gt; repeat pap 6個月後---&gt; 再係ASCUS---&gt; 陰道鏡<br />\n2. 第一次ASCUS---&gt; dna test---&gt; postive就做陰道鏡<br />\n你都做左陰道鏡，無意思啦再test HPV,同埋你ASCUS都係因為HPV<br />\n你依家係擔心佢會唔會演變落去姐都係,咁你應該keep住regular pap smear"},{"pid":"e69906a7d9cdb270c2742b370f6dbf17565f0c79","tid":156350,"uid":88860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T00:49:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>可以做陰道鏡檢查啊你去 （colposcopy)<br />\n連續兩次ASCUS既話</blockquote><br />\n我係私家做pap test之前佢都會隊支野入去撩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後有個mon睇到入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知係咪你講既陰道鏡檢查<br />\n醫生又話我就咁睇係正常<br />\n如果有異常會點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n感謝你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你做個樣聽落係陰道鏡檢查來，但佢係做完pap &quot;smear&quot;之「後」先會做的<br />\n做陰道鏡用d藥水去搵出最異常既部分，再攞組織病理化驗，點都會攞個播，你個陣無？有異常就根據當時情況治療，太多唔講住了<br />\n如果正常既又會再叫返你regular pap smear</blockquote><br />\n咁佢又冇幫我搽藥水喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只係搽左啲gel等我冇咁唔舒服<br />\ncheck完就話正常 然後就攞左分泌物出嚟<br />\n個陣只係拎左分泌物去驗菌同埋幫我做pap smear<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係旺角睇<br />\n加埋塞藥就哂左我$1600<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係好貴<br />\n有冇平啲介紹</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔方便介紹醫生俾你，sorry ah<br />\n公立都唔錯，平麻，你陰道鏡正常唔係急野黎"},{"pid":"3b0a50d7b86b31ad7463a1433e9a1129b07ac9fa","tid":156350,"uid":33991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T00:53:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>可以做陰道鏡檢查啊你去 （colposcopy)<br />\n連續兩次ASCUS既話</blockquote><br />\n我係私家做pap test之前